History
-------

0.2.10 (2022-07-07)
+++++++++++++++++++

* Drop support for Django 2.2 and below,
* Drop support for Python 3.7,
* Python 3.10 support,
* Django 3.2 support,
* enable GitHub Actions,
* remove Travis-CI config. 

0.1.0 (2017-07-20)
++++++++++++++++++

* First release on PyPI.
